  "description": "<b>IDC今天公布预测数据称，PC、平板和智能手机的出货量将在明年上升到17亿台，并且正有着更多走向发展中国家的趋势。17亿台当中的6.62亿台预计会销往中国、印度、巴西和俄罗斯，而美日英等发达国家有望看到6.5亿台左右的出货量。</b>平板和智能手机将带来增长份额中的大部分，预计17亿中会有14亿台智能机和平板，价值约为5000亿美元，而传统PC只有约3亿件，价值低于2000亿美元。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d1746bc/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240648.htm&amp;t=IDC%3APC%2F%E5%B9%B3%E6%9D%BF%E4%B8%8E%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%87%BA%E8%B4%A7%E5%B0%86%E8%B6%85%E8%BF%8717%E4%BA%BF%E5%8F%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240648.htm&amp;t=IDC%3APC%2F%E5%B9%B3%E6%9D%BF%E4%B8%8E%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%87%BA%E8%B4%A7%E5%B0%86%E8%B6%85%E8%BF%8717%E4%BA%BF%E5%8F%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240648.htm&amp;t=IDC%3APC%2F%E5%B9%B3%E6%9D%BF%E4%B8%8E%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%87%BA%E8%B4%A7%E5%B0%86%E8%B6%85%E8%BF%8717%E4%BA%BF%E5%8F%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240648.htm&amp;t=IDC%3APC%2F%E5%B9%B3%E6%9D%BF%E4%B8%8E%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%87%BA%E8%B4%A7%E5%B0%86%E8%B6%85%E8%BF%8717%E4%BA%BF%E5%8F%B0\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http